Seems direct damage spells now do 75% of total hitpoint damage in PvP.  (directly related to manaburn)  While I understand the nerf, I wish verant would consider refunding aa points wasted in this now useless skill of Manaburn.  I would hope this covers SK aa harmtouches and Lifeburn as well.  Had manaburn advertised doing non-resistable damage based on mana up to 75% of the target, I would have spent my points in Spell Casting Fury line.  Im going to petition and email developers corner for a refund.  NOt sure how good it will do, but its worth a shot.  Please do the same if u feel the same way.  Changing what aa skills do after someone have dumped numerous points in it should warrant a refund.<br /><br />-G 
